The Chronicle Bongani Ndlovu, Showbiz Correspondent CELEBRATING the one-year anniversary of her soulful album Songs in the Key of Love, multi-award-winning singer Berita earlier in the day released the music video for Ndikhawulele, the opening track off the album. The music video was premiered on her YouTube channel, this Thursday, as an early Valentines gift to her fans. Meaning meet me in the middle, Ndikhawulele is an intricate look into the emotive relationship between two people who have committed to love. This time Berita tells a love tale of melancholy in a relationship between two people who love each other but yet something is amiss. In the music video this story is told metaphorically through Berita’s performance, lighting and the artistic use of hands to suggest the tension between Berita and her love interest.